    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Kantharoi decorated with panels containing a distinctive pattern of bands having geometric and floral patterns painted with black and added white.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
